  <notepads>
    <notepad>
      <note>Workshop 1: Sentiment Analysis with Ollama

This transformation demonstrates:
1. Reading customer reviews from CSV
2. Building JSON prompts for LLM
3. Calling Ollama API via HTTP
4. Parsing JSON responses
5. Extracting sentiment and scores
6. Writing results to output

Steps Flow:
Input → Build Prompt → Call Ollama → Parse Response → Output</note>
